  "description": "The Peach Tree is a type of fruit tree. It takes 28 days to grow to maturity, after which it will produce one Peach each day during the Summer. It can only grow in the center of a 3x3 square, each square of which must be kept completely clear of objects, flooring, and terrain features (including grass). The 3x3 grid must not overlap the 3x3 grid of another Fruit Tree.",
